'''Suqraṭ''' d afelsafi agrigi n lqern wis semmus send Talalit (ilul ahat di -470/469, yemmut di -399). Yettwassen belli d netta i d-yesnulfan tifelseft tamsirant (morale). Di tilawt ur d-yeǧǧi ara kra n tira, maca tewweḍ-aɣ-d tedmi-s s wudem arusrid seg wa ɣer wa. Amedya, inemladen-is [[Flaṭun]] d Gzinifun refden tamusn-is rnan sseɣren-tt s telqey akken ar yeqqim yisem-is.
